{"ISTHMIAN":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to an isthmus, especially to the Isthmus of Corinth, in Greece.","pos":""}],"ISTHMUS":[{"def":"A neck or narrow slip of land by which two continents are connected, or by which a peninsula is united to the mainland; as, the Isthmus of Panama; the Isthmus of Suez, etc.","pos":""}]}